<p><span style="font-family: Calibri Light; font-size: 12pt;">Key component behind the scenes is of course ARM (<a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/documentation/articles/resource-group-overview/">Azure Resource Manager</a>).<br /> </span></p>

<p><span style="font-family: Calibri Light; font-size: 12pt;">Although you canâ€™t define different access levels on single objects, you have the possibility to delegate Asset-Management to a security department, while still be able to have more Runbook authors contributing to your automation solutions.<br /> </span></p>

